                        <p>9.5 The Customer acknowledges that the Service Provider’s suppliers’ may, if it is of their reasonable opinion that the Customer is abusing the Services or using the Services unlawfully, suspend the provision of the Services without liability on the part of themselves or on the part of Voys Telecom.</p>
