                        <p>12.9 For the purposes of enabling the Service Provider to exercise its rights under this Suretyship, the Surety hereby irrevocably nominate, constitute and appoint the Service Provider to be his agent, with power to sign all such documents and do all such other acts, matters and things as may be necessary to give due and proper effect to the terms of this Suretyship.</p>
